# LogWaveMonitor - Log Frequency & Burst Detector

LogWaveMonitor detects repetitive log events and wave-like error clusters, providing fast visual summaries via CLI.

## Features
- Frequency histogram  
- Timestamp-based grouping  
- Keyword tracking  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/25_LogWaveMonitor.git
cd 25_LogWaveMonitor
python analyze.py
